data.description: Three bedroom brick broad front brick ranch with many updates like Vinyl windows, Kitchen with plenty of Cabinets, and updated flooring, HWFs, door wall to covered patio, Steel entry doors. Whole house Attic fan to keep things comfortable. 1.5 car garage with GDO. Neutral décor throughout, huge laundry room with storage and breakers, and the best part all the appliances stay! All furniture is negotiable. City cert is ordered, purchaser to assume all repairs if any. Owner occupied so all showings are by appointment only. Take a peek you’re going to love it.
